                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260622-28-off132 t18260622-28-cd133"></join>, at St. Luke, Chelsea, 5 pieces of handkerchiefs (each piece containing six handkerchiefs), value 5l., the goods of 
